  "text": "Researchers have also investigated how to design and teach for transfer [CITATION_1] ; thus, as the instructional design literature continues to burgeon, numerous instructional strategies and methods have emerged to facilitate transfer [CITATION_2] . We review key instructional strategies and methods that have been specifically linked to transfer.",
